{"tid":1088000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自願醫保入面，咩叫高風險池?","createTime":"2019-04-01T17:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T18:09:46.000Z","uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94057d1ce5997a5f63d184132b84162b841d8b5c","tid":1088000,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"自願醫保岩岩推出，仲吹到好勁好吸引<br />\n已有疾病又保，又終身續保，又冇保障上限又盛<br />\n但又話唔侵高風險池既人玩<br />\n<br />\n咁咩叫高風險池? 病到點樣先算高風險池?<br />\n<br />\n如果我到時去買自願醫保，<br />\n搞完一大輪，填完表，檢完條賓周<br />\n先話我係高風險池唔受我玩咪仆街?<br />\n<br />\n利申：搵過Google大神，佢幫唔到手，所以轉黎搵連登大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6a2d70688f6258a32ef75db67308ab48aa4f48","tid":1088000,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7027a00ef6df2179692ead17675b288bb8b898e","tid":1088000,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"High risk pool"},{"pid":"e8ab91c071616d1214a5b3f4911c5ab55f4c1d30","tid":1088000,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"有冇保險界/法律界/醫學界既巴絲可以答答我?"},{"pid":"43bd26fecf9f4db33114fd192411bea7a7bae012","tid":1088000,"uid":25133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"講緊有長期病或者病歷<br />\n例如高血壓糖尿或者生過cancer呢啲<br />\n所以你照去投保等佢睇下核唔核保啦"}]}